title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table nested inside a grid cell.
OB: When attempting to export data in a table that is nested inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data in the table should be successfully exported.
SR: To reproduce: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Export data in two tables. Expected result: The data should be exported. Actual result: An exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
